  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE</h2>Explore a living, colorful world, ranging from dense forests to dark caves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/c71c8f358204ccb437dd10040cdd8654.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/c71c8f358204ccb437dd10040cdd8654.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/c71c8f358204ccb437dd10040cdd8654.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD</h2>Your cabin grows with you: build new rooms to unlock additional game mechanics, including cooking, gardening, crafting and sewing.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2d67a716434d81b0f5c6f55aef8ded17.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2d67a716434d81b0f5c6f55aef8ded17.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2d67a716434d81b0f5c6f55aef8ded17.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GROW</h2>Nurture delicate (and delicious) plants in your greenhouse. Eat them raw or make a stew for better nutritional values.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2efc72e78172e8032373dfb5aa65eea0.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2efc72e78172e8032373dfb5aa65eea0.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2efc72e78172e8032373dfb5aa65eea0.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE</h2>Dangerous animals roam some areas in the woods. Better keep a distance if you can. <br><i>(Among Trees also includes a ZEN mode without dangerous animals)</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/4f2610d1eeeebc5a1f96b29823f6c3ce.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/4f2610d1eeeebc5a1f96b29823f6c3ce.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/4f2610d1eeeebc5a1f96b29823f6c3ce.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEST FRIENDS FOREVER</h2>While the wilderness can be dangerous, it doesn't mean you can’t make new friends. Adopt a Fox Pet who you can feed, pet, and train to help you find loot.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/9dfe5b441ffcfcdd71d4ec970ee367e5.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/9dfe5b441ffcfcdd71d4ec970ee367e5.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/9dfe5b441ffcfcdd71d4ec970ee367e5.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE</h2>Explore a living, colorful world, ranging from dense forests to dark caves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/c71c8f358204ccb437dd10040cdd8654.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/c71c8f358204ccb437dd10040cdd8654.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/c71c8f358204ccb437dd10040cdd8654.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD</h2>Your cabin grows with you: build new rooms to unlock additional game mechanics, including cooking, gardening, crafting and sewing.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2d67a716434d81b0f5c6f55aef8ded17.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2d67a716434d81b0f5c6f55aef8ded17.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2d67a716434d81b0f5c6f55aef8ded17.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GROW</h2>Nurture delicate (and delicious) plants in your greenhouse. Eat them raw or make a stew for better nutritional values.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2efc72e78172e8032373dfb5aa65eea0.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2efc72e78172e8032373dfb5aa65eea0.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/2efc72e78172e8032373dfb5aa65eea0.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE</h2>Dangerous animals roam some areas in the woods. Better keep a distance if you can. <br><i>(Among Trees also includes a ZEN mode without dangerous animals)</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/4f2610d1eeeebc5a1f96b29823f6c3ce.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/4f2610d1eeeebc5a1f96b29823f6c3ce.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/4f2610d1eeeebc5a1f96b29823f6c3ce.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEST FRIENDS FOREVER</h2>While the wilderness can be dangerous, it doesn't mean you can’t make new friends. Adopt a Fox Pet who you can feed, pet, and train to help you find loot.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/9dfe5b441ffcfcdd71d4ec970ee367e5.poster.avif?t=1636537260\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/9dfe5b441ffcfcdd71d4ec970ee367e5.webm?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/897730/extras/9dfe5b441ffcfcdd71d4ec970ee367e5.mp4?t=1636537260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
